onDiagnosticsError.prompt:
New diagnostic errors appeared in {{file}}:

{{diagnostics}}

For each error: (1) call getHover at the error position to fetch type info, (2) if the error is a type error, call goToTypeDefinition at that position to navigate to the root type definition, (3) call explainSymbol on the failing symbol if applicable, (4) suggest the most likely fix. Keep response under 20 lines.
